Text.val: Correct overall taxability for manual overrule:
ONLY EXCEPTIONS ARE REGISTERED AS PARTYDEDUCTION !
So if a partydeduction is NOT present, the party is taxable!
If one party has 'an optin' the product is taxable (overrules all exemptions)
All parties must have an exemption for the product to be exempted from tax:
Default taxable value: If one of the parties is taxable, the product is taxable
